1
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,770
Please let me in, Brother.

2
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:54,539
You should show some attitude
when asking for help.

3
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,380
Please let me in, Brother.

4
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,950
After all these years,

5
00:02:01,950 --> 00:02:03,590
you're still so self‑disciplined.

6
00:02:03,590 --> 00:02:04,950
Are you crazy?

7
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,430
Why are you reacting so strongly?

8
00:02:06,430 --> 00:02:07,560
Are you jealous?

9
00:02:08,630 --> 00:02:09,400
Brother.

10
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:12,150
When you get curious about someone,

11
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:15,240
it means you are not far from losing.

12
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,560
Su Xia.

13
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:39,850
Have you ever loved me?

14
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,840
You've never understood me.

15
00:02:44,910 --> 00:02:45,750
Right.

16
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:47,910
Only the high and mighty Mr. Lu

17
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:49,440
can give charity to others,

18
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,870
but you would never condescend

19
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:53,470
to try to understand anyone.

20
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,000
Even in the past,

21
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:57,329
even when you thought
you loved me so much.

22
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,310
What does

23
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:02,910
the past mean to you?

24
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,430
I've forgotten the past.

25
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,980
What about you?

26
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,730
Do you regret it?

27
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,240
I never regret it.

28
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,800
I'm sorry.

29
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:23,360
Mr. Xiao, have some tea.

30
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:25,720
Mr. Jian,

31
00:04:26,310 --> 00:04:27,770
have you made up your mind?

32
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,190
Mr. Xiao.

33
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,600
I want to know

34
00:04:33,830 --> 00:04:35,950
how you'll make sure my family's interests

35
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,350
aren't affected by Lu Fan

36
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,180
throughout this process.

37
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:41,040
Like I said,

38
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,950
I won't take a penny from the Lus.

39
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:45,870
As for the rest,

40
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:47,730
it depends on your own abilities.

41
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:51,280
Mr. Xiao, have you always been
this generous?

42
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:54,270
I've only heard of people
fighting tooth and nail for interests.

43
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:56,670
I've never seen anyone
just give them away.

44
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,040
We want to know

45
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:01,750
why you're doing this.

46
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,320
Of course, I have my reasons,

47
00:05:07,630 --> 00:05:08,950
but I can't tell you.

48
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,390
You only need to focus on

49
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:11,920
your own business.

50
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:16,430
Mr. Xiao,

51
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:18,310
as you know,

52
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,940
trust is the foundation of cooperation.

53
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:23,120
Besides,

54
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,630
Lu Fan

55
00:05:25,750 --> 00:05:28,080
hasn't completely fallen out with us yet.

56
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,920
Hasn't completely fallen out with you?

57
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:33,510
Does this mean

58
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:36,070
you don't want to cooperate with us?

59
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,409
It's not that we don't want to.

60
00:05:38,630 --> 00:05:40,030
We're just a bit worried.

61
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:45,950
Jian Xi.

62
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,920
Su Xia has returned to the Lu family.

63
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:52,480
Mr. Jian,

64
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,750
if I tell Lu Fan

65
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:57,070
that you wanted to hire someone

66
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:58,240
to kill Su Xia,

67
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,560
what will he do?

68
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,630
Su Xia.

69
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:24,200
I've been looking for you.
Why are you here?

70
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,270
Su Xia.

71
00:06:38,190 --> 00:06:40,050
I can see the wounds on your hands.

72
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,400
But tell me, is your heart

73
00:06:43,950 --> 00:06:44,750
still broken?

74
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,630
I know

75
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,040
in the past,

76
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,720
I hurt you in every twisted way.

77
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:12,160
This pain left scars on you

78
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,800
and even deeper scars on me.

79
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:15,920
I'm not kneeling here

80
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:17,870
to beg for your forgiveness.

81
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:21,560
I want to prove and promise

82
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:23,750
that I, Lu Fan,

83
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:26,560
will spend the rest of my life

84
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,390
making it up to you.

85
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,570
I'll love you, protect you,

86
00:07:31,430 --> 00:07:34,090
and cherish your life
as much as I cherish my own.

87
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,360
Su Xia,

88
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,630
marry me.

89
00:07:40,510 --> 00:07:41,510
Give me a chance.

90
00:07:54,870 --> 00:07:55,750
Lu Fan,

91
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:58,360
if one day,

92
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,680
I disappear again,

93
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,850
can you accept that?

94
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,430
Hello?

95
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,720
Mr. Lu, something happened to the group!

96
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,720
Please come over!

97
00:08:29,070 --> 00:08:30,000
Okay, got it.

98
00:08:35,150 --> 00:08:35,870
Wait for me.

99
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:41,750
Lu Fan.

100
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:48,550
Be safe.

101
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:51,720
Okay.

102
00:09:04,150 --> 00:09:06,270
Mr. Lu, it's really serious.

103
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:07,790
The third round of funding
for our project with the Jian Group

104
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:09,990
was supposed to come through next week,

105
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,510
but they just informed us

106
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:12,720
they're delaying the approval process

107
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,510
because

108
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:15,480
they need more time
to adjust their internal processes

109
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:17,030
and reassess the risks.

110
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,790
Delaying it?

111
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,910
At this point?

112
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:23,560
This is already the third payment.

113
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,030
Without that money,

114
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:26,480
our cash flow will dry up.

115
00:09:27,910 --> 00:09:29,910
How much money will I lose every day?

116
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,200
How are we going to pay the suppliers?

117
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,030
What the hell are they doing?

118
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:35,480
I'm not sure.

119
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:36,790
Are they

120
00:09:36,790 --> 00:09:38,650
taking revenge for what happened

121
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,850
between Ms. Jian Xi and you?

122
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:42,670
They wouldn't.

123
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:48,120
It does no good to anyone.

124
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,840
Besides, our cash flow is...

125
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:55,750
Mr. Lu,

126
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,790
we've almost used up
the short-term loan limit

127
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:58,630
from the bank.

128
00:09:59,270 --> 00:10:00,630
And several important partners

129
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:02,960
are having problems with their payments.

130
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,360
It's like they had a deal.

131
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:20,840
Mr. Lu, Mr. Lu!

132
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:22,170
Mr. Jian isn't at home,

133
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,570
and neither is Ms. Jian.

134
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:31,960
Did you find them?

135
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,790
Mr. Lu, I've arrived at the company,

136
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:34,990
but they're not here.

137
00:10:41,510 --> 00:10:42,390
Jian Xi,

138
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:43,750
come out!

139
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:46,200
Mr. Lu, they're really not here.

140
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:47,200
Jian Xi!

141
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,240
Dad,

142
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:23,150
do we really have to go this far

143
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:25,000
with no backup plan?

144
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:28,270
Can we really turn back?

145
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:34,870
Come on, left and right,

146
00:11:34,870 --> 00:11:35,960
everybody!

147
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:40,790
Put your hands up and dance!

148
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:12,040
Has he arranged everything?

149
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:13,480
Rest assured.

150
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:15,870
Then it's your turn to shine.

151
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:16,750
Let's go!

152
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,270
Mr. Lu,

153
00:12:41,510 --> 00:12:43,480
the front desk received an invitation

154
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,280
from Global Capital yesterday.

155
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,550
Global Capital?

156
00:12:55,270 --> 00:12:56,720
Did you check their background?

157
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,480
Yes.

158
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:02,600
Mr. Lu,

159
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:04,720
we can't be picky right now.

160
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,720
They're the only investor

161
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:07,630
that's reached out to us,

162
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,840
and the only one

163
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:09,790
that actually seems capable

164
00:13:09,790 --> 00:13:11,200
of solving our financial problems.

165
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,510
If we miss this chance,

166
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:13,320
there might not...

167
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:15,030
Might not be another one.

168
00:13:20,870 --> 00:13:22,870
Mr. Lu, good to see you again.

169
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:24,240
Sorry,

170
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,510
I didn't tell you

171
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:26,480
I was coming.

172
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:30,510
Zhao Yuan?

173
00:13:30,870 --> 00:13:31,670
Hello.

174
00:13:33,870 --> 00:13:35,870
This is Global Capital. Let's talk.

175
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:46,910
Mr. Lu, I'll get straight to the point.

176
00:13:48,630 --> 00:13:49,490
Leave us alone.

177
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,150
Come on, let's celebrate.

178
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,240
Cheers.

179
00:13:57,790 --> 00:13:59,510
We're signing the contract tomorrow.

180
00:13:59,510 --> 00:14:01,720
The initial funding will be transferred

181
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,670
into Lu Group's account
next week as planned.

182
00:14:03,670 --> 00:14:05,080
They'll use it

183
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:06,960
to pay off their most urgent debts

184
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,560
and some of their suppliers,

185
00:14:08,750 --> 00:14:10,790
buying themselves some time.

186
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:15,250
We'll let them catch their breath

187
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:17,000
and give them some hope.

188
00:14:17,910 --> 00:14:19,320
Once they pin all their hopes

189
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:21,080
on this money

190
00:14:22,390 --> 00:14:23,320
and make plans

191
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:25,550
for the remaining funds,

192
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:28,600
that's when we'll close the net.

193
00:14:32,390 --> 00:14:33,200
Remember,

194
00:14:33,510 --> 00:14:34,750
the rest of the funding

195
00:14:34,750 --> 00:14:36,950
must be released strictly on our terms.

196
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,480
Any minor issue

197
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:40,270
can be a reason for delay.

198
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:43,770
At the same time,
have your overseas partners

199
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:44,720
start spreading

200
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:47,150
bad rumors about the Lu Group.

201
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,200
Mr. Jian.

202
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:54,320
I'm a man of my word.

203
00:14:54,630 --> 00:14:57,000
You'll be greatly rewarded.

204
00:14:57,270 --> 00:14:58,870
Once the Lu Group collapses,

205
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:00,840
we'll make sure the Jian Group takes over

206
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:03,390
its most valuable businesses.

207
00:15:03,630 --> 00:15:04,480
Mr. Xiao,

208
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:06,870
you're indeed a man of your word.

209
00:15:08,510 --> 00:15:09,200
Mr. Xiao,

210
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:11,650
you asked me to keep an eye on Lu Fan.

211
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:13,630
And he really did something.

212
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:15,000
After signing the contract,

213
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:18,390
possibly due to some pressure,

214
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:23,630
he borrowed money from a loan shark.

215
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:38,840
Did Lu Fan propose to you?

216
00:15:42,910 --> 00:15:43,910
Well done, Su Xia.

217
00:15:44,030 --> 00:15:46,240
This is perfect.

218
00:15:48,390 --> 00:15:50,120
Lu Fan is completely in the trap now,

219
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,390
and all of his assets

220
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:52,850
will vanish in an instant.

221
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:54,840
When he's drowning in despair

222
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:56,270
and has nothing left,

223
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:59,600
you'll be the final straw
to break him down.

224
00:16:00,390 --> 00:16:01,240
Leave him.

225
00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:06,360
Xiao Qi,

226
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:13,950
do you have to force him to death?

227
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:21,200
Su Xia,

228
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:23,720
Have you forgotten how we survived

229
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:25,240
these years?

230
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:27,910
Have you forgotten how the Lu family

231
00:16:27,910 --> 00:16:29,240
forced our two families to death

232
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:30,480
and ruined our lives?

233
00:16:31,790 --> 00:16:32,670
This blood debt

234
00:16:32,670 --> 00:16:34,790
must be paid with his destruction!

235
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:37,270
Su Xia.

236
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:45,020
We've been planning carefully
and enduring every humiliation for years

237
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:46,980
just for this moment, haven't we?

238
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:51,670
Think about it.

239
00:16:53,510 --> 00:16:54,630
Don't let me down.
